text: Torny is a municipality in the district of Glâne in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2004, the former municipalities of Middes and Torny- le-Grand merged into the municipality of Torny.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 19 July 2011 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Glâne
